1.1.0
------------------
- Replaced old licence by PHPDoc style licence
- Implemented an "Amazon ID" datatype for ASIN search in content edit. 
  Can be automatic on publish or contributor can search via a button in edit interface, through custom HTTP action
- Added i18n support (with 4.3+ API) - NOT COMPATIBLE WITH eZ Publish versions < 4.3
- Added extension.xml (eZ Publish 4.4)
- Fixed problem with products URLs that were not URL decoded

1.0 beta
------------------
Initial beta release